WEBVTT

00:36.136 --> 00:38.438
WHAT WOULD YOU DO
IF AT THE MOMENT OF DEATH

00:38.505 --> 00:40.073
A VOICE FROM
THE DARKNESS

00:40.140 --> 00:42.008
OFFERED YOU A CHANCE
TO LIVE AGAIN ?

00:42.075 --> 00:43.376
HAVE YOUR ANSWER ?

00:43.443 --> 00:44.878
THERE'S NO TIME
TO THINK ABOUT IT,

00:44.944 --> 00:46.746
YOU'RE A HEARTBEAT
AWAY FROM FLATLINING.

00:46.813 --> 00:48.748
QUICK,
WHAT'S THE ANSWER ?

00:48.815 --> 00:51.151
I'M TODD McFARLANE,
AND I CREATED "SPAWN".

00:51.217 --> 00:53.653
I HOPE YOU'LL CONSIDER
THE QUESTION I JUST POSED,

00:53.720 --> 00:55.722
BECAUSE A MAN NAMED
AL SIMMONS DIDN'T.

00:55.789 --> 00:57.690
WHEN THE QUESTION
GOT POPPED ON HIM,

00:57.757 --> 01:00.326
HE SIGNED LIKE
SOME STUPID ROOKIE IN BLOOD,

01:00.393 --> 01:03.229
SEE, AL HAD QUALITIES
HE DIDN'T EVEN KNOW HE HAD,

01:03.296 --> 01:05.398
A SPECIAL KIND OF WIRING,
THAT<i> MALEBOLGIA,</i>

01:05.465 --> 01:07.033
THE DEVIL LOOKS FOR.

01:07.100 --> 01:08.868
WHEN HE SAID "YES"
TO THAT VOICE,

01:08.935 --> 01:12.138
HE SIGNED ON FOR A LOT MORE
THAN HE BARGAINED FOR.

01:12.205 --> 01:15.008
SO BEFORE YOU FIND YOURSELF
IN A SIMILAR SITUATION,

01:15.074 --> 01:17.577
AND A VOICE CALLS
TO YOU IN THE DARKNESS,

01:17.644 --> 01:19.946
THINK OF AL,
OR AS YOU MAY SEE,

01:20.013 --> 01:23.550
YOU'LL HAVE ALL ETERNITY TO
THINK ABOUT YOUR MISTAKE TOO.

01:23.616 --> 01:27.353
AND NOW "SPAWN",
SO TURN OFF YOUR LIGHTS.

01:28.688 --> 01:32.792
Captions made possible by
HOME BOX OFFICE

01:32.859 --> 01:36.062
A DIVISION OF TIME WARNER
ENTERTAINMENT COMPANY, L.P.

02:29.415 --> 02:32.485
FOUR HUNDRED YEARS
HAVE PASSED.

02:32.552 --> 02:36.723
ONCE AGAIN, IT IS TIME
FOR A NEW WARRIOR TO EMERGE

02:36.789 --> 02:39.559
FROM THE DARKNESS.

02:44.831 --> 02:46.699
THROUGHOUT TIME,

02:46.766 --> 02:49.168
THE BATTLEFIELDS
HAVE CHANGED.

02:49.235 --> 02:52.839
BUT THE PRIZE HAS ALWAYS
REMAINED THE SAME...

02:52.906 --> 02:55.141
THE HUMAN SOUL.

03:25.872 --> 03:27.707
TAKE OUT YOUR
PRESS I.D.,

03:27.774 --> 03:29.876
I WANT HIM TO
SEE WE'RE LEGIT.

03:29.943 --> 03:32.045
THIS IS UGLY SHIT WE'RE
TALKING ABOUT, BENNETT.

03:32.111 --> 03:34.881
IF WE GET VERIFIABLE
INFORMATION

03:34.948 --> 03:37.150
AND WE GOT THE BYLINE
OF THE DECADE !

03:37.216 --> 03:39.118
I KNOW.

03:39.185 --> 03:40.420
THIS WAY.

03:40.486 --> 03:42.789
YOU KNOW WE'RE SCREWED
IF HE DOESN'T SHOW.

03:42.855 --> 03:44.090
RELAX, HE'S
A GOOD SOURCE.

03:44.157 --> 03:46.125
NOW DO ME A FAVOR,
TAKE A VALIUM

03:46.192 --> 03:47.894
