ME CRAZY.

03:47.961 --> 03:49.295
MR. STEVENS ?

03:50.496 --> 03:53.666
I'M DAVE BENNETT,
THIS IS KENNY HAYES.

03:55.201 --> 03:57.170
WE SPOKE ON THE PHONE.

04:05.645 --> 04:07.413
LOOKS LIKE...

04:07.480 --> 04:09.449
YOUR MEETING'S
BEEN CUT SHORT.

04:09.515 --> 04:11.384
GOD !

04:15.088 --> 04:16.756
OH GOD !

04:16.823 --> 04:18.858
GOD AIN'T HERE BOY,

04:18.925 --> 04:21.194
