YOUR ANSWER, SMART BOY.

05:02.568 --> 05:05.905
NO ONE, I DIDN'T
TELL ANYBODY ELSE.

05:05.972 --> 05:07.874
DON'T LIE TO ME,
SMART BOY.

05:07.940 --> 05:09.075
DON'T YOU PISS ME OFF

05:09.142 --> 05:10.777
BY TRYING THAT
CRAP WITH ME.

05:16.082 --> 05:19.852
EACH WARRIOR'S BORN
AS A CLEAN SLATE,

05:19.919 --> 05:21.788
KNOWING NOTHING.

05:21.854 --> 05:24.691
THE ONLY INSTINCTS
WHICH THEY CAN ACT UPON

05:24.757 --> 05:26.793
ARE DRAWN
FROM THEIR PAST.

05:38.037 --> 05:40.306
SO ?

05:40.373 --> 05:44.077
HE'S SEE NO EVIL,
HEAR NO EVIL,
SPEAK NO EVIL.

05:44.143 --> 05:46.979
GOOD, LET'S DO
THIS THING AND GO.

05:52.485 --> 05:54.954
DON'T DO THIS,
YOU DON'T HAVE TO.

05:55.021 --> 05:59.325
