LIFE INSURANCE.

06:09.635 --> 06:11.537
( male )
LET HIM GO.

06:14.807 --> 06:16.576
JESUS !

06:52.979 --> 06:54.447
AHH !

07:08.094 --> 07:09.796
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU ?

07:18.771 --> 07:20.173
STAY BACK !

07:20.239 --> 07:22.809
YOU DON'T WANT
TO DO THAT.

07:29.182 --> 07:31.417
HELP ME !

07:42.161 --> 07:44.330
I LOVE YOU, AL.

07:52.738 --> 07:56.142
OH NO, I CAME
BACK FOR YOU !

07:57.510 --> 07:59.245
