THEIR PROPER ESCORT.

08:14.460 --> 08:16.796
OH MAN,
I LOVE IT.

08:18.664 --> 08:20.933
ESPECIALLY THE GENT WITH
HIS HEAD ON BACKWARDS !

08:21.000 --> 08:24.570
THAT IS SWEET.

08:24.637 --> 08:26.639
CHECK HIS SHORTS,

08:26.706 --> 08:28.407
I BET THEY'RE
BRIMMIN' OVER !

