08:51.097 --> 08:52.565
WHAT DO YOU
THINK, SPAWN ?

08:52.632 --> 08:54.400
SPAWN ?

08:56.335 --> 09:00.206
YEAH, AS IN
HELL, SPAWN.

09:01.874 --> 09:03.776
HEY, IT'S WHAT
YOU ARE, BABY.

09:03.843 --> 09:06.445
SO GET USED TO IT.

09:06.512 --> 09:08.514
DID I DO THIS ?

09:08.581 --> 09:10.483
INSTINCT,
SWEETHEART.

09:10.549 --> 09:13.286
YOU'RE A KILLER !

09:13.352 --> 09:16.055
BORN AND BRED.

09:16.122 --> 09:19.191
YOU SEE VIOLENCE,
YOU ACT.

09:19.258 --> 09:22.194
IT'S A GIFT.

09:22.261 --> 09:25.164
THAT'S WHY
HE PICKED YOU.

09:27.433 --> 09:30.002
I CAN'T REMEMBER
ANYTHING.

09:30.069 --> 09:32.271
WHAT'S WRONG
WITH ME !?

09:33.873 --> 09:36.609
TOO LONG UNDER THE TANNING
BOOTH BY THE LOOK OF IT.

09:49.121 --> 09:52.058
AHHH !

10:01.734 --> 10:03.803
