FROM THE MAELSTROM.

11:33.692 --> 11:35.795
GET OUT OF MY WAY,
OLD MAN.

11:35.861 --> 11:39.799
YOU DON'T REMEMBER,
IT DOESN'T MATTER.

11:39.865 --> 11:43.602
IT'S WHAT YOU LEARN NOW
THAT'S IMPORTANT.

11:43.669 --> 11:46.505
