12:51.570 --> 12:53.973
TONY TWIST IS GONNA
NEED SERIOUS DRUGS

12:54.039 --> 12:55.608
WHEN HE FINDS OUT.

12:55.674 --> 12:58.244
THESE THREE BOZOS
WERE HIS BEST HITTERS.

12:58.310 --> 13:00.179
SO...

13:00.246 --> 13:02.815
ONE OF THESE THINGS
IS NOT LIKE THE OTHERS.

13:02.882 --> 13:05.151
WHAT'S HIS STORY ?

13:05.217 --> 13:06.886
DAVID BENNETT,

13:06.952 --> 13:08.854
JOURNALIST WITH
THE WASHINGTON POST.

13:08.921 --> 13:11.090
