THE ALLEY'S FAR END.

13:11.157 --> 13:14.226
EXCEPT BENNETT'S WON A PULITZER
FOR HIS INVESTIGATIVE PIECE

13:14.293 --> 13:17.429
ON THE CONGRESSIONAL SCANDAL
THREE YEARS AGO.

13:17.496 --> 13:19.698
IF IT AIN'T ON<i> ESPN</i>
I COULDN'T GIVE A SHIT.

13:19.765 --> 13:21.100
NO, SIR.

13:21.167 --> 13:23.202
( helicopter buzzing )

13:26.906 --> 13:29.542
OKAY, SO WE GOT TWO DEAD
REPORTERS FROM WASHINGTON.

13:29.608 --> 13:31.443
THREE DEAD HITTERS
FOR TONY TWIST,

13:31.510 --> 13:33.179
WHAT ABOUT THE
OTHER STIFF ?

13:33.245 --> 13:35.848
HOMELESS,
NO I.D.,

13:35.915 --> 13:38.083
HIS PRINTS
CAME UP NIL.

13:38.150 --> 13:40.186
PROBABLY JUST AN
ALLEY MUSHROOM

13:40.252 --> 13:41.987
POPPED UP AT
THE WRONG TIME.

13:42.054 --> 13:45.291
ANOTHER VERBAL
ACE, SIR.

13:46.458 --> 13:47.726
TWITCH ?

13:47.793 --> 13:48.861
SIR.

13:48.928 --> 13:50.696
FIND ME A CONNECTION
BETWEEN ALL THESE TOE-TAGS,

13:50.763 --> 13:52.264
BUT FIRST,

13:52.331 --> 13:54.099
FIND ME SOME WITH
CHOCOLATE SPRINKLES.

13:54.166 --> 13:55.634
