13:55.701 --> 13:58.237
HALF THAT, YOU KNOW
I'M ON A DIET.

14:33.005 --> 14:34.406
( honking )

14:37.776 --> 14:39.211
( voices )
THAT'S YOUR BEST FRIEND...

14:39.278 --> 14:40.546
... BEST FRIEND....

14:43.649 --> 14:45.517
HERE'S TO AL SIMMONS,

14:45.584 --> 14:48.721
THE BEST FRIEND A POOR
NUMBER PUNCHIN' JERK LIKE ME

14:48.787 --> 14:50.089
COULD EVER HAVE.

14:51.223 --> 14:53.626
( girl )
DAD...

14:53.692 --> 14:54.560
WAIT, HONEY.

14:54.627 --> 14:55.527
DADDY.

14:55.594 --> 14:58.130
SOMEONE WANTS
TO SAY GOODBYE.

14:58.197 --> 14:59.665
BYE BYE,
DADDY.

14:59.732 --> 15:01.667
SEE YOU LATER,
SWEETNESS.

15:06.839 --> 15:09.742
