HAPPENED TO ME !?

15:44.543 --> 15:48.380
IT'S HELL'S PLAN
TO KEEP THE NEW RECRUITS

15:48.447 --> 15:50.149
CONFUSED,

15:50.215 --> 15:53.452
HOPING TO DISCOURAGE
THE WARRIORS OF ANY

15:53.519 --> 15:56.055
PERSONAL MISSION.

15:56.121 --> 15:58.324
OH, PLEASE !

15:58.390 --> 16:00.259
