GETTING ALL BENT OUT OF SHAPE

16:00.326 --> 16:02.161
OVER A WOMAN !

16:02.227 --> 16:04.363
OKAY, SO SHE WAS
THE LOVE OF YOUR LIFE

16:04.430 --> 16:05.931
AND THE ONLY THING
THAT MATTERED TO YOU

16:05.998 --> 16:07.633
IN THIS
WHOLE DISGUSTING,

16:07.700 --> 16:10.169
PUTRID, LITTLE UNIVERSE.

16:10.235 --> 16:12.805
OKAY, SO NOW YOUR
FORMER BEST FRIEND COMES IN

16:12.871 --> 16:15.007
AND THE AMIGO IS
PUTTING IT TO HER

16:15.074 --> 16:17.109
ON A REGULAR BASIS.

16:17.176 --> 16:19.311
