16:27.519 --> 16:29.121
IT'S ROCKY ROAD.

16:30.556 --> 16:32.257
GET AWAY FROM ME.

16:32.324 --> 16:33.892
YOU CAN'T BLAME
HER THOUGH.

16:33.959 --> 16:36.528
AFTERALL,

16:36.595 --> 16:39.498
YOU'VE BEEN DEAD
ALMOST FIVE YEARS.

16:40.366 --> 16:41.700
YOU'RE LYING.

16:41.767 --> 16:43.736
IF I'M LYING
I'M DYING,

16:43.802 --> 16:45.504
WHICH WOULD BE
KIND OF REDUNDANT.

16:45.571 --> 16:47.339
ANYWAY SPAWN,

16:47.406 --> 16:50.109
YOUR FORMER SELF, MEANING
ONE HELL-BENT FOR LEATHER,

16:50.175 --> 16:52.978
KICK-ASS, TAKE NO PRISONERS,
GOVERNMENT ASSASSIN

16:53.045 --> 16:55.714
BY THE NAME OF
AL SIMMONS,

16:55.781 --> 16:57.483
IS DEAD.

16:57.549 --> 16:59.918
IT'S NOT TRUE !

16:59.985 --> 17:02.388
