THE BEST PART YET.

17:06.592 --> 17:08.394
DON'T YOU WANT TO KNOW
WHERE YOU'VE BEEN ?

17:08.460 --> 17:10.863
YOU DID ASK, SO
YOU MUST WANNA KNOW.

17:10.929 --> 17:13.599
LOOK, BACK OFF !

17:13.665 --> 17:16.168
BEFORE I PERMANENTLY
INTRODUCE YOUR FACE

17:16.235 --> 17:17.803
TO YOUR COLON.

17:20.472 --> 17:23.909
YOU KNOW, YOU'RE
KINDA CUTE,

17:23.976 --> 17:26.512
WHEN YOU GET ALL
INDIGNANT LIKE THAT.

17:27.746 --> 17:30.816
YOU GOT NOWHERE
TO GO, SPAWN.

17:30.883 --> 17:32.885
DON'T YOU WANT TO KNOW WHERE
YOU'VE BEEN ALL THIS TIME ?

17:32.951 --> 17:34.153
