YOU COULDN'T GIVE HER

17:52.771 --> 17:55.707
AND A HUSBAND WHO'S STILL
WEARING HIS FACE.

17:55.774 --> 17:58.677
WHAT DO YOU
GOT,<i> CHAR</i> BABY ?

17:58.744 --> 18:01.246
WHAT DO YOU GOT ?

18:12.724 --> 18:15.027
HELP ME.

18:15.093 --> 18:18.397
GODAMMIT,
I'M NOT DEAD.

18:18.464 --> 18:20.399
I'M NOT HERE.

18:22.668 --> 18:24.002
THE NEW SPAWNS

18:24.069 --> 18:27.072
EACH TRIED TO DENY
WHAT THEY'D BECOME,

18:27.139 --> 18:30.075
HOPING THAT
A SMALL SPARK OF TRUTH

18:30.142 --> 18:33.011
WILL AWAKEN THEM
FROM THEIR NIGHTMARE.

19:08.747 --> 19:12.818
