HAPPEN TO ME ?

20:22.955 --> 20:26.325
YOU MADE A DEAL, YOU
STUPID SON OF A BITCH.

20:26.391 --> 20:29.595
YOU MADE A DEAL
WITH<i> MALEBOLGIA.</i>

20:32.130 --> 20:35.467
YOU CUT A DEAL
FOR YOUR SOUL.

20:39.371 --> 20:42.441
