YOU SEE WANDA

20:42.507 --> 20:44.876
AND THEN BECOME
HELL'S SPAWN.

20:44.943 --> 20:48.080
A RANKING OFFICER
IN THE DEVIL'S ARMY.

20:48.146 --> 20:50.382
WELL NOW
YOU'VE SEEN HER.

20:53.719 --> 20:57.022
TIME TO
PAY THE PIPER.

21:00.859 --> 21:02.260
GET OFF ME !

21:11.303 --> 21:13.271
NOW CAST
FROM HELL,

21:13.338 --> 21:15.374
THE WARRIOR'S
CROSSED PATHS

21:15.440 --> 21:18.977
WITH THEIR OWN DEMONS
IN HUMAN FORM.

21:29.855 --> 21:33.225
( male )
Those scumbag,
douche bag eating,

21:33.291 --> 21:36.228
motherfucking,
cocksucking shits !

