Motherfucking prick !

21:38.163 --> 21:41.066
I'll take your fucking
head and chop it off !

21:41.133 --> 21:44.670
CALM DOWN, TONY.

21:44.736 --> 21:47.005
JUST TELL ME
WHAT WENT WRONG ?

