TRYING TO PULL ON ME, HUH ?

22:03.689 --> 22:06.258
I MEAN WE'RE TALKING
ABOUT MY BEST HIT MEN

22:06.324 --> 22:08.293
GETTIN' MERCILESSLY
WHACKED OVER HERE !

22:09.327 --> 22:10.762
HOW AM I SUPPOSED TO
DEAL WITH THIS ?

22:10.829 --> 22:12.497
THEY WERE AMBUSHED,
SNIPERED, WHAT ?

22:12.564 --> 22:15.767
THEY'RE NOW WEARING
THEIR HEADS ON BACKWARDS

22:15.834 --> 22:17.335
IS WHAT I'M SAYING.

22:17.402 --> 22:19.738
Their bones get pretzeled
by somebody who knows

22:19.805 --> 22:22.107
how to do it
right.

22:22.174 --> 22:23.508
I SEE.

22:23.575 --> 22:25.644
I SEE TOO.

22:25.711 --> 22:27.579
I SEE YOU ASKING ME
TO DO YOU A FAVOR

22:27.646 --> 22:30.682
and suddenly my cleaning crew
gets taken out by some asshole

22:30.749 --> 22:33.018
WHO THINKS HE'S
THE TERMINATOR.

22:33.085 --> 22:36.254
I'M SENSING AN
ACCUSATION HERE, TONY.

22:36.321 --> 22:37.889
ALL I'M SAYING IS,

22:37.956 --> 22:39.591
THIS SMELLS
LIKE THE WORK OF

22:39.658 --> 22:42.027
A GODAMN GOVERNMENT
TRAINED ASSASSIN !

22:42.094 --> 22:45.864
AND THAT JUST HAPPENS
TO BE YOUR STOCK IN TRADE.

22:47.132 --> 22:49.267
IT WASN'T
ANY OF MINE.

22:49.334 --> 22:50.902
AND IF I WERE YOU,

22:50.969 --> 22:53.205
I'D BE VERY CAREFUL
ABOUT THE NEXT TIME

22:53.271 --> 22:54.940
I MADE SUCH STRONG
IMPLICATIONS

22:55.006 --> 22:56.942
WITHOUT THE FACTS.

22:57.008 --> 22:59.644
SO WHAT ABOUT
THE JOURNALISTS ?

22:59.711 --> 23:01.913
Tomorrow's
a bitch.

23:01.980 --> 23:03.081
GOOD.

23:03.148 --> 23:04.583
YEAH FOR YOU.

23:04.649 --> 23:07.886
THIS SHIT'S
COST ME BIG TIME.

23:07.953 --> 23:10.756
YOU'LL BE AMPLY
COMPENSATED FOR YOUR LOSS.

23:10.822 --> 23:12.290
LET ME KNOW

23:12.357 --> 23:14.726
WHAT YOU FIND OUT
ABOUT THIS MYSTERY ASSASSIN.

23:14.793 --> 23:18.897
I'LL SEND YOU HIS LIVER AND
MAYBE A COUPLE OF FINGERS.

23:23.602 --> 23:25.871
( telephone dialing )

23:25.937 --> 23:28.073
Hello.

23:28.140 --> 23:30.075
THE NEWSMEN HAVE
BEEN DEALT WITH.

23:30.142 --> 23:31.543
Who did you use ?

23:31.610 --> 23:33.478
MAFIA ELEMENTS,
NOTHING TRACEABLE.

23:33.545 --> 23:36.681
Good, thank you.

23:36.748 --> 23:39.317
AND AS WE
DISCUSSED...

23:39.384 --> 23:41.820
The appropriations
are already in place.

23:41.887 --> 23:44.289
As of now you've got
unlimited credit

23:44.356 --> 23:46.358
with The Department
of Defense.

23:46.424 --> 23:48.193
I APPRECIATE
THAT, SENATOR.

23:48.260 --> 23:49.961
Believe me,
it was worth it.

23:50.028 --> 23:51.496
Now I'll feel
free to call

23:51.563 --> 23:53.465
if there are any
further complications.

23:53.532 --> 23:55.167
OF COURSE,
BUT TELL ME,

23:55.233 --> 23:57.369
HOW LONG DO YOU
INTEND TO COVER FOR HIM ?

23:57.435 --> 23:59.938
As long as
I have to.

24:00.005 --> 24:02.240
HE'S A CHILD KILLER.

24:02.307 --> 24:03.642
Look we've been
through this before--

24:03.708 --> 24:04.910
you don't have a son,

24:04.976 --> 24:06.611
let alone one you
can give your name to.

24:06.678 --> 24:09.681
So what he does is
my problem, understand ?

24:09.748 --> 24:11.349
THESE JOURNALISTS
WON'T BE THE LAST.

24:11.416 --> 24:13.218
YOU CAN'T KEEP THIS
QUIET FOREVER.

24:13.285 --> 24:16.721
Yes I can, you see, the
dead keep their secrets.

24:19.691 --> 24:21.827
( sirens )

24:26.965 --> 24:29.501
OKAY MAN,
WHAT'D I DO ?

24:29.568 --> 24:32.037
SHUT UP AND GET YOUR
ASS ON THE GROUND NOW !

24:32.103 --> 24:34.239
WHAT'D I DO, MAN ?

24:34.306 --> 24:38.210
IF IT ISN'T OFFICER HECTOR
FROM INTERNAL AFFAIRS.

24:38.276 --> 24:39.511
YOU KNOW WORD IS,

24:39.578 --> 24:41.713
YOU TOLD THE CAPTAIN
WE'RE SKIMMING OFF THE TOP.

24:41.780 --> 24:43.748
LISTEN, IF YOU CAN'T
KEEP YOUR MOUTH SHUT,

24:43.815 --> 24:44.482
WE'LL SHUT IT FOR YOU !

24:44.549 --> 24:46.551
WHAT KIND
OF SHIT IS...

24:52.157 --> 24:53.625
WHY IS IT THAT
PEOPLE WITH AUTHORITY

24:53.692 --> 24:55.727
ABUSE THEIR POWER ?

25:22.787 --> 25:24.956
WORD OF ADVICE,
OFFICER...

25:26.091 --> 25:27.826
RETIRE.

25:34.165 --> 25:38.236
THAT'S IT SPAWN,
LET YOURSELF GO.

25:38.303 --> 25:41.506
GET PISSED,
DO SOME DAMAGE !

25:41.573 --> 25:43.842
DON'T TAKE SHIT
FROM NOBODY !

25:43.909 --> 25:46.278
AND OH YEAH,
THE BIG BOY DOWNSTAIRS.

25:46.344 --> 25:49.147
'CAUSE THIS IS THE
WAY THE WORLD ENDS.

25:49.214 --> 25:51.917
NOT WITH A BANG,

25:51.983 --> 25:53.919
BUT A LOT OF BLOOD
AND TORN FLESH

25:53.985 --> 25:55.387
AND BROKEN BONES !

25:55.453 --> 25:58.657
AND I JUST LOVE IT.

26:03.228 --> 26:06.698
AN SO THE GAME
HAS BEGUN, AGAIN.

26:07.933 --> 26:09.668
AFTER FOUR HUNDRED YEARS,

26:09.734 --> 26:12.203
A NEW WARRIOR
TAKES CENTER STAGE,

26:12.270 --> 26:15.273
PREPARING FOR
THE GREAT BATTLE.

26:15.340 --> 26:19.911
AND WITH HIM
COMES PAIN, DEATH,

26:19.978 --> 26:23.315
AND THE VILE STENCH
OF BRIMSTONE.

